  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TransmitPower>

    public enum TransmitPower
extends java.lang.Enum<TransmitPower>
implements java.io.Serializable
    The transmit power enum of the beacon.
    The coverage of the LEVEL0 is minimum, and the coverage of LEVEL11 is maximum.
    Not all values apply to all kinds of beacon. For more details to see https://github.com/Sensoro/SDK-Android.
